# Review Rules

## Responsibility

Block merges that violate SDD, Specs, or safety.

## Must reject when

- Feature code lacks Product + Specification linkage
- Architecture-changing PR has no Architecture/ADR update
- Secrets, credentials, or `.env` (non-example) are included
- Behavior diverges from Spec without Spec update
- Scope creep unrelated to the task is bundled in

## Must verify

- Acceptance criteria addressed
- Tests mapped to Specs (or explicit manual test notes)
- Docs updated when behavior/design changed
- CHANGELOG updated for user-visible releases (when releasing)

## Review output

Use `docs/templates/Review_Template.md` for non-trivial reviews.
